summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6134 for the improvement of West Rose Street from 45th Avenue Southwest to 46th Avenue Southwest; and certain other streets, avenues and alleys; by constructing sewers and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 85344, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
